'''Oliver Cockford''' (July 30, 1902 - April 27, 1954) was an American journalist and actor from St. Louis. 

==Early life and education==
Oliver was born in St. Louis to photographer Alyssa Cockford (1871 - 1952) and stay-at-home dad DeAndre Cockford (1871 - 1944). 

